title: 10 More Books - January 2016 (gnv64)
description:
Another collection of 10 books for this month, 6 PDFs and 4 ePUBs:

01. A Companion to Intellectual History by Richard Whatmore and Brian Young
02. A Wealth of Common Sense - Why Simplicity Trumps Complexity in Any Investment Plan
03. Carnal Knowledge - Baxter's Concise Encyclopedia of Modern Sex
04. Clinical Communication in Medicine by Jo Brown, Jane Kidd, Lorraine Noble and Alexia Papageorgiou
05. Easy and Delicious Camp Cooking: Trip Pocket Guide by Dick Borden
06. Keynote - Professional Presentations and Animations by Angelo Spiler
07. Microsoft Excel Essential Hints and Tips - Diane Griffiths
08. The Cambridge Introduction to Jane Austen (2nd Ed)
09. The Gender Quest Workbook - A Guide for Teens and Young Adults Exploring Gender Identity
10. The Ghost in My Brain - How a Concussion Stole My Life
